cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as person re-identification, attribute classification, body part segmentation, and pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses multi-task learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes a method for combining multiple datasets, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the application of the proposed method in mobile robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper deals with visual understanding, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
